mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.store.index

Class NullIndex

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.store.index.PrimaryIndex
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.core.store.index.NullIndex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable, Index<MultiDimensionalNumericData,MultiDimensionalNumericData>

    public class NullIndex
extends PrimaryIndex
    This can be used as a pass-through for an index. In other words, it represents an index with no dimensions. It will create a GeoWave-compliant table named with the provided ID and primarily useful to access the data by row ID. Because it has no dimensions, range scans will result in full table scans.
